generated_description: aes, legally known as aes s.a., is a company based in jasło, subcarpathian voivodeship, specializing in the import and distribution of heating, sanitary, and installation systems. established in october 1991, aes s.a. offers a comprehensive range of products including boilers, stoves, underfloor heating systems, sanitary ceramics, and various plumbing and electrical fittings. the company collaborates with a network of hundreds of suppliers to provide a diverse product portfolio, ensuring high-quality materials with certifications and approvals. operates a corporate showroom and a hydro-market store, catering to both wholesale and individual customers.
